{"tid":1577226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非入一入嚟 真black bloc保護手足同其他街坊","createTime":"2019-09-17T15:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T01:56:31.000Z","uid":236878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9abc986c9bef176352f6b3e737861f67242aaa7e","tid":1577226,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cuErsLo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcuErsLo.jpg&h=204486f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申:圖係隔離post見到 但有少少嘢想補充 我明未必個個夠膽 因為示威日子帶gear 雖然唔犯法 但的確有機會畀狗咬 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過希望手足可以試下下面基礎版</span>零風險先(可能有狗會截查):<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基礎版:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑色背囊 入面唔一定放gear/物資 可以放其他嘢 總之塞到個背囊表面睇落漲</span><br />\n(因為發夢聽人講剩係帶gear 少量急救用品 雨褸 加套替換衣物 個袋已經好滿)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁做起碼可以掩護其他入場的手足<br />\n但行完麻煩就盡快離場返屋企/離開現場 總知唔好食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以的話就街坊裝出嚟幫手做哨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者等離場時候 出嚟接應手足<span style=\"color: red;\">(依然帶住個好望落好漲的黑色背囊)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">進階版</span> (詳細睇下面link)<br />\n同上 不過帶備少量急救用品(for自己用)<br />\ne.g. 梳打水(記得要label係用嚟做咩/寫低比例) 因為比例唔同有唔同用途 <br />\n紗布 等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">終極和理非</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係買埋gear <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">買同持有防護裝備係唔犯法 但有機會畀狗咬</span> 不過越多人咁做個風險就會越低 其實間中都有人唔係衝嘅時候帶gear:例如法律界遊行 人鏈 <br />\n仲有2個例子比較特別: 大J 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\nbtw 依家tg成日放我覺得就算係街坊 買返set保護自己都好合理 識人買咗set畀屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家狗放tg越嚟越嚟癲 如果手足自備gear 同急救物資 起碼可以自保同埋遇到突發放tg 唔會太混亂 e.g.狗亂放tg 隔離有街坊<br />\n誤中 如果大家都咁做就可以幫手減低物資同fa壓力<br />\n<br />\n梳打水 稀釋洗頭水比例: <br />\n(梳打粉同水1:1可以用嚟洗顏料水)<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.lihkg.com%2Fthread%2F1217785%2Fpage%2F1&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5ID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=3895ccf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\ngear:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gU0qsqF0_qg9f-vF9BKu3zZ2rfz5pxtuz57PY2Vo30M/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1gU0qsqF0_qg9f-vF9BKu3zZ2rfz5pxtuz57PY2Vo30M%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5ID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=b0a898e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gU0qsqF0_qg9f-vF9BKu3zZ2rfz5pxtuz57PY2Vo30M/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5ID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=00ecb640\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n以上全部係share我有參考過又覺得實用的link <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實唔需要太擔心搶裝問題 當gear全民普及嘅時候手足就唔駛一定要掉裝 同埋有需要嘅時候 你哋可以畀有需要的手足 咁掉咗裝嘅就唔駛又出去買</span><br />\n<br />\n頭盔:不過60926好似真係有d缺 可以買其他濾罐組合<br />\n利申:剩係買過2次裝 以上內容如有錯漏請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f657bdb174b7442e5d13dec4269cddd8df14f6a5","tid":1577226,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"4bdeb5be93c45382fb0b48e7b504895d4a652370","tid":1577226,"uid":236878,"like":